## ðŸ“Š Project Overview
This Power BI project provides an executive-level analysis of **sales performance, customer behavior, and salesperson effectiveness**.  
It is designed to help decision-makers track KPIs, analyze trends, and evaluate performance across products, customers, and regions.

The focus of this project is on **data modeling, DAX calculations, dashboard design** rather than the raw dataset itself.

