## ðŸ“„ Dashboard Pages

### 1ï¸âƒ£ Executive Sales Overview
This dashboard provides a high-level view of overall sales performance.

**Key Metrics**
- Total Net Sales  
- Total Quantity Sold  
- Average Order Value (AOV)  
- Average Discount %  
- Year-over-Year (YoY) Growth  

**Key Insights**
- Monthly sales trends by category  
- Net sales and quantity distribution by city  
- Top-performing products  

![Executive Sales Overview](Template/Executive_Sales_Overview.png)

---

### 2ï¸âƒ£ Customer & Salesperson Performance
This dashboard focuses on customer segmentation and salesperson analysis.

**Key Analysis**
- Customer segments (Active, Occasional, VIP)  
- Net sales and quantity by category  
- Geographic distribution of sales  
- Salesperson performance relative to discount rates  
- Top 10 products by net sales  

![Customer and Salesperson Performance](Template/Customer_and_Salesperson_Performance.png)

